Data Farmer

The Data Farmer is different.

The crop is information.

Objective

Grow high-quality information rather than merely collect it.

Fields

Wild Fields

Raw internet.

High volume.
Low trust.

Managed Fields

Communities.
Experts.
Repositories.

Moderate volume.
Higher quality.

Greenhouses

Experiments.
Internal testing.
Structured observation.

Low volume.
Very high quality.

⸻

Data Farming Loop

Observe → Capture → Clean → Label → Connect → Compress → Store → Rehydrate → Reuse

Instead of asking:

“How much data do we have?”

The Data Farmer asks:

“How fertile is this information ecosystem?”

